            Broken Top Mountain
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300">
            Stunning alpine peaks and wilderness trails
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 italic">
          🏔️ Based in Bend, Oregon • Where outdoor adventure meets cutting-edge
          technology
